snippet.title: Yellow Taxi Goes Vroom - Six One Indie Showcase Trailer
snippet.description: Get a fresh look at Yellow Taxi Goes Vroom in this trailer for the arcade platformer game. Explore retro worlds without a jump button in this love letter to the N64 era of collectathons. The trailer also reveals the free Rat update will be available on September 24, 2024. Yellow Taxi Goes Vroom is available now on PC.
